              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer843070309016075847">I started reading this book before I went to Peru, and I was connecting with it. It is totally possible that I was distracted by trip preparations, etc. I picked up the book again at the end of my trip (when my Kindle, which had been malfunctioning on vacation, miraculously started working again.) And then I got totally absorbed. The landscapes of Peru were brought to life, and the mystery sucked me in!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


